{"tid":2205896,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"女社工被指荃葵青遊行拒出示身分證被控阻差辦公 罪名不成立並獲訟費","createTime":"2020-09-17T06:29:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-17T07:36:11.000Z","uid":240362,"like":38,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"3e14987d51c48bdef0755b22ed581b5e953f3792","tid":2205896,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T06:29:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/9519\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F9519&d=WBhgCLuhUD%2FUeH80S3I9%2BggLKV3biakQup4fopcqKIo%3D&h=19e310ab\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/9519</a><br />\n<br />\n#西九龍裁判法院第十四庭 <br />\n#黃雅茵裁判官  <br />\n#裁決<br />\n#0825荃灣<br />\n<br />\n林(22)<br />\n<br />\n控罪：<br />\n(1)阻撓在正當執行職務的警務人員<br />\n(2) 未能在規定下出示身分證明文件（交替控罪）<br />\n<br />\n【速報】<br />\n兩項罪名不成立，並獲得訟費"},{"pid":"ab900f79348db63538d77fb647b5bc7b9ddd34d7","tid":2205896,"uid":362346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T06:29:36.000Z","msg":"la"},{"pid":"ea057d9ac4d228a4121944bbc310a0f6d6c83168","tid":2205896,"uid":274532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T06:29:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85e8e27d7a27538f9ece216662c70f0deeba2428","tid":2205896,"uid":240362,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T06:30:20.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"red\">去年8月25日荃葵青遊行後爆發警民衝突，期間女社工被指拒絕出示身份證，更要警員先出示委任證。女社工被控阻差辦公，及未能在規定下出示身份證明文件的交替控罪。經審訊後今（17日）在西九龍法院被裁定兩罪均不成立。裁判官黃雅茵指被告在警員要求後43秒，便從錢包取出身份證，時間不屬不合理，而市民亦有權向警員出示委任證，認為她不是自招嫌疑，批出辯方訟費申請。<br />\n<br />\n22歲被告被控於去年8月25日在荃灣街市街和眾安街交界，阻撓女督察梁敏儀執行職務。控方案情指，女督察梁敏儀當晚穿上防暴裝巡經現場時見到有人聚集，並見被告大叫「黑警」，她上前截查時，被告多番拒絕出示身份證，又反過來要求她出示警察委任證。<br />\n<br />\n女督察梁敏儀在庭上指，由於她當時穿着制服，又認為若出示委任證便會妨礙警方工作，故當時沒有應被告要求出示警方委任證。<br />\n<br />\n不過，裁判官裁決時指，根據《警察通例》，除了在例外情況外，若市民要求警員出示委任證，警員便需要出示，身穿制服並不能成為理由，而這個要求也不會構成阻撓。<br />\n<br />\n此外，現場片段顯示，警方要求被告出示身份證後，被告在約43秒後便取出一個黑色銀包，並手持身份證。裁判官認為合理時間並不代表最短時間，43秒亦不能說是超過合理時間。雖然被告曾大聲說話，但她沒有辱罵他人，考慮到現場人聲嘈雜，故這也不能說成阻撓。</span></strong>"},{"pid":"2a8fc03de2a5d05c6a4c6de7eaf8714dd0f24dbb","tid":2205896,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ab900f79348db63538d77fb647b5bc7b9ddd34d7","tid":2205896,"uid":362346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T06:29:36.000Z","msg":"la"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T06:30:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a4b9864aba5cb19aedbbdeda664eb006b7ceb89","tid":2205896,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ea057d9ac4d228a4121944bbc310a0f6d6c83168","tid":2205896,"uid":274532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T06:29:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T06:30:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1df24a7a3c6620e008368006fe7555899cf205a0","tid":2205896,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T06:31:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94d8466033990dd2ebafc51f74e47ae19d989f3b","tid":2205896,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1df24a7a3c6620e008368006fe7555899cf205a0","tid":2205896,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T06:31:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-0